"""Dokima — Multi-agent orchestration engine.
Usage: dokima "Feature description" [project_dir]
       If project_dir is omitted, uses current working directory.
Flow: Strategist → User Clarifications → Strategist Refine → TL Spec Pre-Review → Orchestrator Gate → Human Gate → Coder(branch) → vet(validate) → nm(adversarial+PR) → Tech Lead(spec review) → Report
Output: Live to terminal + saved to /tmp/dokima-output.txt
